Package language.java

Package containing the generator of java code.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    JavaDecorationTable
    Java class for generating Decoration Table's java code Reflect the model's DecorationTable class Call appendCode(String, Stringbuffer) to generate code
    JavaElement
    Generate the java code for an Element
    JavaGenerator
    Entry point for generating a java code for a given SeedTransducer and DecorationTable
    JavaGeneratorErrorTypesTest  
    JavaGuard
    Java code generator for a DecorationTable's guard Generate a lambda function, and add it into a Hashtable by the name of the impacted variable
    JavaSeedTransducer
    Java code representation of a SeedTransducer
    JavaState
    Java code of a State Basically an if statement of the state followed by many instructions depending on the current index value
    JavaUpdate
    Java code of an update of a DecorationTable
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    JavaComparator
    Java generation of a Comparator (eg. equals, less than, greater than, less or equals, greater or equals)
    JavaGeneratorErrorType
    Generation possible error types enumeration
    JavaSemanticLetter
    Java code representation of an ArcSemanticLetter Convert all letters into java-compatible letters
